div.p:
(a) The withdrawals and transfers of the military forces,
                    equipment and supplies of the two parties shall be completed within three
                    hundred (300) days, as laid down in Article 2 of the present Agreement;

(e) The Joint Commission and the International Commission
                    shall ensure that steps are taken to safeguard the forces in the course of
                    withdrawal and transfer;

The points of entry into Viet-Nam for rotation personnel and replacements of material are fixed as follows:
—Zones to the north of the provisional military demarcation line: Laokey, Langson, Tien-Yen, Haiphong, Vinh, Dong-Hoi, Muong-Sen;
—Zone to the south of the provisional military demarcation line: Tourane, Quinhon, Nhatrang, Bangoi, Saigon, Cap St. Jacques, Tanchau.
